<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head id="code"></head>
<style>
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 0 !important }
body {
border-bottom: 5px solid;
border-image-source: url("https://i.stack.imgur.com/1WlsT.png");
border-image-slice: 50% 50% 50% 50%;
border-image-width: 12.5px;
border-image-repeat: repeat;

}
</style>
<body id="run" >
</body>
</html>
